 * Dependencies:
 *   - LibTorch (PyTorch C++ API): https://pytorch.org/cppdocs/
 *   - OpenCV:                     https://opencv.org/
 *
 * Build example (CMake):
 *   find_package(Torch REQUIRED)
 *   find_package(OpenCV REQUIRED)
 *   target_link_libraries(your_target ${TORCH_LIBRARIES} ${OpenCV_LIBS})
 */

